Class SMRCommandWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.corfudb.runtime.smr.SMRCommandWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SMRCommandWrapper
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This is used by SMREngine to wrap commands before serializing them in the stream, so that it can add its own header information.
